Meet OBWS Founders Club member Angela Brown, Founder of D'Serv Healthy Hair Care (@DservHealthyHair). Her company specializes in plant-based treatments and products for hair loss such as alopecia, stress issues, and damage from protective styles.⁠
⁠
'I need to be around other Black business owners who know how hard it is out here. Belonging to a community of entrepreneurs allows me to ask the tough questions...' - Angela Brown⁠
⁠
Join the OBWS Founders Club today to connect with ambitious Black founders like Angela! Click the 🔗 in bio or head to founders.obws.com 👈🏾
